                <note rend="inline" type="source">800.711/74: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Winant</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-03-17T16:00:00-04:00"
                            >March 17, 1944—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2021. For Phillips. Embassy’s 1878, March 8, 5 p.m. Our feeling is that
                    censorship should be based solely on military considerations and should not be
                    used for any other purpose.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
